// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2812 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: c0a56d78-17c6-5699-92b6-b0b735c6b736

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
